Title: Mr. Muscles!
Description: A man, almost entirely naked save for a single shoulder pad, some pants, and what appears to be a blindfold or perhaps a low bandana. He is here to show these wretched beasts how the icon of male masculinity struggles against his surroundings until they better suit himself. If he were an animal, those who raise beasts would refer to him as a patriarch. The whole world will tremble before Mr. Muscles, OR HIS NAME IS NOT MISTER MUSCLES! MISTER MUSCLES FOREVER!
